entries.femaleVariant: Ugh, sure is a scorcher. The power's out again, I can't even get a fan goin'.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="はあ、本当困るわよね。水も出ないし。でも仕方ないから。ところで新しい仕事はどう？" t="Oof. Tell me about it. Water's out, too. But what can you do, you know? How's things in the new job?" b="" a=""/>
Barely keepin' up with all those orders. But at least I get to take the leftovers home.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="へえ、何かいいのがあったら分けてよ。食べ物はいつでも大歓迎よ" t="Oooh. Well, if you get your hands on something good, you know I'm always hungry." b="" a=""/>
Nah, I don't touch the ganic stuff. Small portions, and what's there is gross. Took some home once, we all got sick.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="コックが中に唾入れてたりして" t="I bet if someone orders fresh, the cooks just spit in it." b="" a=""/>
Hell, I'd spit too, if I wasn't afraid they'd trace my DNA. Or catch me on camera.
